[I] Windowing library for the Xfce4 desktop

[T] Libxfce4windowing is an abstraction library that attempts to present
[T] windowing concepts (screens, toplevel windows, workspaces, etc.) in a
[T] windowing-system-independent manner.

[U] https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/libxfce4windowing/start

